    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion is beginning to soften, add your<strong> arborio rice</strong> with the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and cook for 1 min, stirring to coat the grains of rice in the oil</p><p>Add your<strong> Chinese rice wine</strong> and cook for 30 secs</p><p>Add the <strong>vegetable stock</strong> a ladle at a time, stirring occasionally, for 20-25 min</p>",
